Azure Virtual Desktop provides enhanced security features such as:

* Multi-Factor Authentication
* Role-based access control
* Data isolation

For example, sensitive data remains in Azure instead of being stored on local devices.

# Real-Life Use Case:
A real-life use case is financial institutions ensuring secure remote access.

# Real-Life Example:
Another example is preventing data leakage in remote work setups.

Security features make AVD suitable for sensitive workloads.
